level 0
keywords help
---
Syntax: help [topic]

Displays the help entry for a given topic. If no topic is provided, the
summary help page is shown.

Help lookup first tries an exact match, then a prefix match. So "help ba"
will find "bash" if no exact match exists for "ba".

Related help commands:
  shelp <topic>   -- Staff reference for skills and spells (detailed
                     mechanical information, class acquisition, effects).
  rhelp <topic>   -- Help on races and racial traits.
  sthelp          -- Help on combat stances and their effects.
  rmlist          -- List and describe racial modifiers.
  lore <object>   -- Lore information about items found in the world.

Topic categories you can explore:
  commands        -- Lists available commands by category.
  slist           -- Full list of spells and skills by class.
  rlist           -- Lists available races.
  socials         -- Lists available social commands.
  summary         -- Overview of the game and newbie guidance.

See also: commands slist rlist socials summary
